metadata.name: Welcome, I’ve been waiting for you. ( Not a cult)
metadata.description:
I have arrived after a long lonesome journey
So many reasons to give up
To let the darkness in
My one companion 
Pressed warmly to my heart
Reminding me of better days to come
One foot in front of the other
I kept going
Now I’m here
The traveler and the destination
It was always one and the same
